sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Start as Opportunity change
  participant Bpmn as Maestro BPMN
  participant Agent as Coded Agent
  participant Outlook as Outlook
  participant Bridge as Azure Function bridge
  participant Approver as Approver
  participant Log as Data Fabric

  Start->>Bpmn: Start instance (payload)
  Bpmn->>Agent: plan (evaluate + draft)
  Agent-->>Bpmn: disposition, recommendation, approver chain
  alt disposition == auto_clear
    Bpmn->>Log: Record auto_cleared
  else disposition == needs_approval
    loop per approver in chain
      Bpmn->>Agent: render card
      Bpmn->>Outlook: send Adaptive Card
      Outlook->>Approver: card delivered (task open)
      alt decision within SLA
        Approver->>Bridge: click Approve or Reject
        Bridge->>Bpmn: CompleteAppTask (resume)
        Bpmn->>Agent: process_response decides next action
      else SLA breach
        Bpmn->>Outlook: reminder and set escalated
      end
    end
    Bpmn->>Outlook: notify requester
    Bpmn->>Log: record agent rec vs human decision
  end
